{"tid":2044374,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【香港的傷痕】一名大學生的「四仔」——上Gear、被捕、求醫、見官","createTime":"2020-05-31T05:27:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-31T10:46:02.000Z","uid":54517,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"de7e456162241691e2e7e46e82ef32bb19cee4f3","tid":2044374,"uid":54517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T05:27:19.000Z","msg":"阿然身邊的人常形容他是個理性、冷靜的人，被拘留期間，他確實擔心別人多於擔心自己。保釋出來後，他覺得自己和以前沒甚麼分別，直至一週後才開始發現自己有點不妥：他看直播不單會感到憤怒，還會心跳加速、出冷汗和全身顫抖；他的專注力變得很差，完全無心處理學業；他變得難以控制情緒，對家人發脾氣的次數多了。某次吵架中，他的母親說了一句「我唔想成為第二個周梓樂阿媽」，讓他感覺憤怒又不解，失落了好一陣子。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1073976?fbclid=IwAR0AozJdJX3W9irCEiYY1V5JMngT-SLPe9Fc-jHXPzG7k-zWmz1DHmS_juo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1073976%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0AozJdJX3W9irCEiYY1V5JMngT-SLPe9Fc-jHXPzG7k-zWmz1DHmS_juo&d=zeAGpz59Z2vRp%2Fz3xPaAdBR1GjkmqS0yYYF7Sw2QOJY%3D&h=a600a42f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1073976%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0AozJdJX3W9irCEiYY1V5JMngT-SLPe9Fc-jHXPzG7k-zWmz1DHmS_juo&h=fd8cacab\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1073976?fbclid=IwAR0AozJdJX3W9irCEiYY1V5JMngT-SLPe9Fc-jHXPzG7k-zWmz1DHmS_juo</a><br />\n<br />\n手足,加油"},{"pid":"0acaa48b4bd0ce81d11ec50de31ce50b54e5480d","tid":2044374,"uid":54517,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T05:36:08.000Z","msg":"他覺得「向前看」的心態很重要：「當你睇住越來越多人被捕，被捕唔再係一件新鮮事，就會叫自己唔好咁執著，要努力向前看，否則唔會諗到下一步點做。」他同意，一年後的抗爭氣氛冷淡了，但覺得只能孤注一擲，繼續想辦法延續抗爭，直至徹底「攬炒」：「刀拮唔中肉唔識痛，要用震撼教育叫醒大家。」"},{"pid":"f49b0bebed40b531f8632a8d50fc55a3435dcf23","tid":2044374,"uid":235535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T05:38:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa329a96e25231d8de36bd775cfcd9648af19867","tid":2044374,"uid":54517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f49b0be